name: Dallas/Fort Worth International Airport from FL350 ᴴᴰ
description:
Okay, that's a big airport. I was watching the live map on my seat back intently, hoping to catch a view of DFW as we descended into Houston. Sorry about any blurriness, my window was pretty scratched up :/ Hope you enjoy, nonetheless, and don't forget to vote for my next video! :D

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
